  "description": "A nighttime aerial view of a city skyline illuminated against a dark body of water. A long bridge, lit with white and red lights, stretches across the water towards the cityscape. The city itself is a dense cluster of buildings, with prominent skyscrapers standing out. The buildings are lit with warm yellow and cool white lights, creating a vibrant contrast against the dark sky. In the foreground, there are scattered lights indicating residential or suburban areas. The overall composition suggests a vast urban landscape extending into the distance.",
